bio: Fathers on fleek 🔥 Submit a #fashiondad to fashiondads@gmail.com or DM 👴🏼👔 and shop our cool shit! ⬇️

posts.caption: You guys are the first to get a glimpse at my new jacket, sent to me by #TomFord himself! This is part of his #SpringSass collection, which explains the fabulous #fringe flair on an otherwise simple #LeatherJacket. Mark my words -- fringe is so hot for spring, especially for #Coachella and all the other festivals I'll be hitting. 😎💃🏼 Normally I would wear this jacket with some relaxed fit #Wranglers and my white #NewBalance sneakers, but it actually does pair well with these chic #plaid trousers. I'm definitely runway-ready (per usual)! 😊 #OOTD #Couture #FringeForSpring #IDontPopMollyIRockTomFord #DesignerFashion #FirstLook #Trendy #Chic #PlaiddyIssues #FashionDads via @yerrawizardkim

Happy #Humpday, fashionistas! 🕺🏻🐫 Today I’m bringing new flavor to “business casual” with this sleek and sassy ensemble. I’ve paired a classic pinstriped button-down with a fashionable yet functional pair of #UnderArmour athletic shorts to allow me greater mobility around my home office while still looking chic. 😊 But the footwear is what really takes this lewk to the next level —my signature #Gucci loafers complimented with a nice mid-calf white sock is a bit unconventional, but it always pays off to take a #FashionRisk! 💁🏼 And of course I topped everything off with a tasty bourbon cocktail. Hey it’s 5 o’clock somewhere!! 😉 #OOTD #BusinessCasual #ChicLewks #WhoWhatWear #FashionBlogger #Athleisure #ProtectThisHouse #GucciGang #HappyHourStyle #FashionDads via @keallen329

Budweiser, more like Studweiser amirite? 😏💁🏼🔥 Feeling so #blessed on this Christmas Day and wishing all my fellow fashionistas a very stylish celebration! I’ve been saving this stunning sweater especially for today, and have paired it with a classic pair of #VanHeusen black slacks and an understated gray collared blouse for a more structured look. I stood next to the tree for a extra splash of color, and take note of my flattering pose. You don’t have to be a seasoned #FashionBlogger to look like this — just stand tall and confident like the diva you are! 💃🏼Merry Christmas and #DillyDilly to all my fans and followers! 🍻 #OOTD #FestiveFashion #Studweiser #HolidayLooks #SweaterWeather #WhoWhatWear #MerryAndBright #BodyConfident #BlogLife #FashionDads via @atlfish

What an ahhh-mazing #FathersDay! 😍 I got to relax all day long in one of my favorite lewks. To be completely honest with you guys, I can’t really do rompers because of my long torso, but pro tip: you CAN mimic the romper vibe with a matching short and blouse. 💁🏼 I chose this stunning tropical print (limited edition #TommyBahama, of course) in a bold green hue with subtle pops of pink and red. Feel free to tuck in your top or let it hang free —whatever accentuates your figure best. 😉 And I completed this holiday ensemble with a classic fedora in a neutral color, and my signature #Toms #StunnerShades. Hope all my fellow fashionista fathers had a fabulous day as well! 🙌🏻 #OOTD #FathersDayFlow #RomperVibes #TropicalPrints #LegsForDays #BeachReady #SummerSwag #WhoWhatWear #FashionBlogger #RompHim #FashionDads via @ape.real

Sneak peek from my photo shoot today 😉 I can't wait to show you guys all my new looks on the blog! This is just one of my favorite outfits for Spring 2017 -- a lime green #RalphLauren blouse straight off the #NYFashionWeek runway paired with a stunning khaki cargo short from #Kohls' couture collection. This ensemble is classic yet trendy and the versatility is just FABulous! 💅🏻 And I have to shout out @Nike for sending me these brand new, limited edition #AirMax trainers in one of spring's hottest hues: Mermaid Blue. 🙌🏼🐟 I like to keep it edgy by not tying the laces. 😎 Stay tuned for more #StyleGoals on the blog! #OOTD #FashionBlogger #ModelVibes #PhotoShoot #StreetStyle #SpringFashion #StraightOffTheRunway #BoldColors #ClassicChic #FashionDads via @matt_johnston

Running a company and fashion blogging on the side is definitely hard work, but SO rewarding, and I just love being able to create a stylish #WorkLook every day! 😊 The key is to stay on trend but maintain your comfort, which is why I always wear my signature #CrocsWithSocks for footwear. They are so versatile, whether I'm dressing up in khakis and a polo or doing a sportier look like this crisp #Columbia button-down with a sleek #Asics performance short. I always wear a ball cap with my company logo and I have them in 16 different colors to go with every outfit (true fashionistas don't play around when it comes to color coordination 😜). I hope my look inspires you to reach your full potential at work today! #OOTD #WorkAttire #CEOflow #FashionBlogger #BossBitch #FootwearOnFleek #Athleisure #CornerOfficeVibes #BoldColors #SpringStyle #WhoWhatWear #FashionDads via @jess_c_short
Last call for #FathersDay gear for your rad dad or #TrophyHusband! 🏆👴🏼 Order now @literallybuying with expedited shipping for guaranteed arrivals by Dad’s Day! Link in bio

Red, white and BOOM, I am looking good! 💁🏼😎💥 You guys know today is my absolute FAVE holiday to flaunt my signature #AllAmerican style and yes, mixing Stars and Stripes prints once again! #SoEdgy 🇺🇸🇺🇸 I have tucked a stunning patchwork polo into a relaxed fit #TommyBahama short -- drawstring for extra comfort (and will come in handy when I dive into the BBQ later 😜). And because I love to keep my fans guessing, I traded in my signature white #NewBalance trainers for a subtle pop of neon with these contemporary #Topsiders. 🎾👟To complete the look, a cowboy-Panama hybrid hat straight off the runways, sassy stunner shades, and my 24-karat golden boy! 🐶 And like I even need to tell you guys -- always match your tailgate chair to your ensemble! Happy 4th of July, everyone! 🇺🇸😎 #OOTD #RedWhiteAndBoom #FreedomFashion #HolidayHauteLooks #MixingPrints #FlagsOnFleek #DoggyStyle #FashionDads via @lizadunning @pj_dunning

Brrrr it's cold in here, there must be some fashion in the atmosphere! ❄️💅🏻 You guys know I love #WinterLooks and most of all.....LAYERING! 🙌🏼 When it's this cold, the more layers the better and a trendy winter coat is key, like this custom @canadagoose piece -- yes they make denim jackets for celeb clients only (thanks Rihanna! 😉). Underneath, you'll see a chic chef's jacket and seersucker pinstriped pants (of course I'm wearing #Lulu leggings as my base layer for extra warmth and comfort). And to top it off, a stunning ski hat that truly has it all -- fur flaps, fluffy pompom, AND sassy braids. I'm ready to brave the elements in style! #OOTD #LoveYourLayers #SnowStyle #CanadaGoose #DenimDiva #RiRi #FurOnFleek #FashionIcon #DressToImpress #FashionDads via @mtthwmcphrsn

Strolling into the week in STYLE! 💃🏼💃🏼 I am so excited to show off this #StreetChic look as I jet off to Miami for a little business and pleasure. ✈️🌞 A lot of my fans have been asking me how to wear shirts with holes and I'm here to help! The key is to go full couture because only the top designers can get this look right -- this is a distressed tee straight from the #Givenchy runway that you can never go wrong with. But I've paired it with a basic #Columbia short to let the blouse be the focus of the ensemble. As for accessories, I have a sturdy yet stylish belt to clip my passport on (#TravelHack!) and a bold cerulean ball cap that says "I'm ready for some fun in the sun!" 😊 My athletic footwear has me prepared for anything, and remember -- always pair a white sneaker with a classic black crew sock! Cash me in South Beach! 😎 #OOTD #FashionBlogger #TravelStyle #AirportCouture #RunwayReady #MiamiHeat #SouthBeachStyle #SummerLooks #WhoWhatWear #FashionDads via @zachjlangston
Last call for #FathersDay gear! 👨🏻👴🏻 Order by 11:59pm tomorrow (June 6) for guaranteed delivery by the holiday. Link in bio + FREE 🇺🇸 shipping! @literallybuying

Ready to cook this #Thanksgiving turkey and doing it in fun and flirty style! 😊 I love getting a little silly on holidays and debuting a fashionable #StatementApron like this one I picked up on the Jersey Shore boardwalk last summer. The trick is to find a piece that both compliments your complexion AND enhances your figure. 💁🏼 And I’ve paired this outfit with my favorite pair of house loafers for a little extra sass. Now let’s get cookin! 🔥 #OOTD #ThanksgivingStyle #HolidayLooks #StatementPiece #KissTheCook #ThighGap #BodyPositive #ConfidentCouture #WhoWhatWear #FashionDads via @douglasharry24

Back by popular demand: Our rosé/brunch campaign shirts! Because you should never stop fighting for what you believe in. 🍾🍾🍳🥓 These are super soft, quality AF tees and we have a tank as well. Shop @literallybuying (link in bio) and FREE 🇺🇸 shipping! #MakeAmericaBasicAgain

#MarchDadness is one of my favorite times of year, and an AMAZING opportunity to show off your #SportsStyle! 💁🏼🏀 As you may be able to tell, I am rooting for my alma mater #Michigan (GO BIG BLUE!) and have chosen to do a bold and contemporary head-to-toe ensemble. I have paired a classic #Adidads track pant with a stylish and breathable long-sleeved top (tucked in and slightly bloused out for the most flattering effect). And always remember that a stripe down your pant leg elongates those lovely legs. 💃🏼 To complete the look, a trendy pair of blue and yellow sneakers, and my favorite accessory -- a swanky sun visor. 😎 Cash me on the court! 😜 #MarchMadness #MarchDadness #sweet16Stye #SportySpice #MichiganBasketball #BlueAndYellow #BoldColors #Chic #Trendy #CourtsideCouture #FashionDads via @crabbytabi

Apologies to all my fans that I haven't posted in a while! I've just been living it up this summer -- in high fashion of course! 😎🔥 Today I'm at Six Flags showing off a fun and flirty look and I just happened to come across this colorful sign that coordinates with it! 🤣 As you know, I LOVE a chic cargo short and fanny pack combo, because you can never have too many pockets for a day at the theme park. I especially love that this FP is XL -- so much more room for all my essentials! 👛 But the highlight of this outfit is definitely my limited edition #CherryGarcia tie-dyed tee. Yes you CAN be a #Fashionista and a #Deadhead! 😜 To complete this head-turning ensemble, I took a standard crew sock and rolled it down for a trendier throwback vibe, and paired them with my signature #Asics sneakers which allow me to walk all day in style and comfort. 👟👟 See you on the Ferris wheel, fam! 💁🏼 #OOTD #SixFlagsSwag #SummerStyle #CasualCouture #FannyPackinHeat 🔥 #FashionBlogger #WhoWhatWear #TanAndTrendy #StyleAndComfort #FashionDads | @bfeldmar @jfeldmar

Sundays are for multitasking! I'm getting some housework done, indulging in a little #WineTime, AND showing off my #SpringStyle....at the same damn time! 😜😎 I am so excited to show you guys this trendy but playful apron I purchased from my favorite local boutique, Island Time. 🌴🕰 Because this statement piece is so bold and colorful, I have paired it with a neutral khaki from head to toe -- a stunning sleeveless polo from #EddieBauer and a class #OldNavy cargo short. A chic grey #Ugg moccasin completes this weekend look. I am sipping in style! 🍷🤗 #OOTD #SpringLookBook #SundaySwag #VaVaVacuum #Tropicool #FashionBlogger #WhatIWore #LoveMyWine #WeekendFlow #FashionDads via @stoneyqueen

The most stylish season is officially here! 🙌🏼😎 You guys know I LOVE #SpringFashion like no other -- you can show off all your assets in chic, flirty outfits and you're not sweating through them. 💁🏼 Today I'm doing an ultra trendy look with a graphic tank top tucked into high-waisted #CargoShorts from #Aeropostale and a bold black belt. I just love a short that comes up to your natural waist; it accentuates your figure more than you realize! For footwear, I have taken my signature #CowboyBoots to the next level with a high navy sock to match my tank, and I am loving the results. And of course, to top it all off.....my fabulous #CowboyHat. Never underestimate the power of accessories! 👒 Happy spring, y'all! 🌞 #OOTD #StepIntoSpring #SeasonForStyle #CowboyCouture #ChicTrends #FashionBlogger #CargoLife #WhatIWore #FashionDads via @ejseigel

Whoopsie, I’m a couple days behind on the Santa calendar but you can get away with anything when you look this good! 💁🏼🔥 I absolutely LOVE dressing festive for the holiday season and showing off some of my favorite trends. Cats are so hot right now, as are pom-poms, so this sweater could honestly not be more en vogue. 💃🏼 I added a little extra sass with this fashionable Santa hat, and while you can’t see them, you can rest assured I’m wearing my signature relaxed-fit Wrangler jeans and classic Nike Monarchs. 👟👟 Happy holidays, my fellow fashionistas! 😘🎅🏼 #OOTD #WhatIWore #FestiveFashion #HolidayLooks #ChristmasCouture #SantaSwag #SweaterWeather #WhoWhatWear #FashionBlogger #FashionDads via @_volere_bene

Strutting into the weekend like 💃🏼😎💁🏼👠 Fashion never sleeps and I am definitely staying woke! This is one of my favorite looks because it blends casual and couture with a little touch of humor. 😜 I have paired a below-the-knee #Aeropostale plaid short with one of my favorite custom tees and draped a classic #LLBean button-down over it for a dapper layered look. But the footwear and accessories are what really elevates this outfit. YES these are fabulous #Ferragamo loafers and I have paired them with a neon athletic sock like the risk-taking trendsetter that I am! I added my favorite #PanamaHat from #Orvis, slung on my #Hermes #ManBag, and of course, rocking my stunner shades. 😎 And one of my secret #StyleTips: wear a #VIP lanyard as a necklace so you always look like you're heading somewhere important. 💁🏼 #VIPlife #OOTD #StreetStyle #SpringFashion #WeekendFlow #StayWoke #FashionBlogger #MadForPlaid #AccessoriesAreEverything #FootwearOnFleek #WhoWhatWear #FashionDads via @isobelj

Summer isn't over yet, and I'm stretching my fab summer style as long as I can! 💁🏼😎 This is one of my absolute favorite looks because of the impeccable color coordination right down to the footwear. 😊 I have paired a chic #Adidads athletic top in a bold coral hue with a versatile black #Champion short, and matched the ensemble PERFECTLY with these custom-made water shoes. It's not easy being a #FashionBlogger but somebody has to do it! 💅🏻 I threw on a camo ball cap with a kiss of coral for a little extra sass, and completed the look with a #VeraBradley carryall in a trendy power print. I can take this look to the beach, the gym, or even a business lunch at Chili's. Enjoy the last couple weeks of summer, fellow fashionistas -- and don't forget your sunblock! 🌞 #OOTD #SummerStyle #WhatIWore #ColorCoordination #FashionWeek #AllAdidadsAllTheTime #Athleisure #LoveYourBody #FashionDads

Fashion goals: holiday edition! 🎉🎉 I love dressing for patriotic occasions and today I am doing an extra glam look with these stylish suspenders instead of a traditional belt to keep my trousers up. 😎 First step is to pair a timeless pair of black suspenders with contemporary denim like these distressed Levi's. Next, select a statement blouse and tuck it into your jeans to accent your figure. I die for this vintage #AmericanFlag tee from #RalphLauren's Retiree Collection. 🇺🇸🇺🇸 And to keep the look chic but still practical, I've thrown on my #Asics all-purpose shoes -- you can never go wrong with fresh footwear like this. Happy #MemorialDay, friends! #OOTD #HolidayStyle #StatementPieces #DenimDiva #CasualChic #MultipleAngles #FashionBlogger #WhatIWore #USA #FashionDads via @kristasintz

Total eclipse = total fashion! 🌘🕺🏻 I soaked up all the science in style AND safety today, donning a chic pair of #SolarEclipse glasses with a contemporary yet whimsical outfit, featuring my signature #Costco cargo pants (spoiler alert: they DO zip away to shorts! 💃🏼) and an exceptionally breathable tee from #LululemonMen. And as my fans know, I AM a #GadgetGuy, so I stay strapped with my #GoPro, headset, and a satchel full of devices and chargers -- never leave home for a major event without them! 😊 To complete this look, I threw on a sassy ball cap, and a fashionable yet functional pair of #Brooks trainers. Hope you all watched the #SolarEclipse with as much swag as I did! 😎 #OOTD #WhoWhatWear #FashionBlogger #SolarStyle #CargoCouture #CostcoPro #BreakawayPants #GadgetGoals #FashionDads via @lilliangraycharles

Footwear on fleek! 😎 I am obsessing over my new Z-Coil sneakers and here to show you guys that pain relief footwear CAN still be fashionable and fabulous! 👟👟 I went with the classic #Freedom style in navy and white and just love how they pair with my favorite striped pajama onesie from #Sears #SleepCollection (I never stop being stylish, even when I'm snoozing). 😴 When I take Snowflake for a walk later or grab the newspaper in the morning, I'm going to be the talk of the cul-de-sac. 😊 #WhoWhatWear #FashionableFootwear #Zcoil #OrthopedicStyle #SpringSneakers #PajamaJam #SleepStyle #FashionBlogger #NighttimeLooks #FashionDads

Good morning from the Yacht Club! ⚓️ I am so excited to show off this new look today -- I call it "90s rodeo beach chic", which not everyone can pull off, let me tell you! 💁🏼 I started with a pair of distressed, relaxed fit #Wranglers and a classic black #CalvinKlein tee (and my monogrammed belt buckle of course). But instead of stopping there, I added a billowy white button-down for that signature #SouthBeach style (also very reminiscent of any Michael Bolton video in the early '90s, which was a peak fashion era). 🙌🏼 Instead of cowboy boots, I chose an all-purpose #Rockport sneaker, which is boat-approved! And to complete the look, a #boho beach hat with a touch of rustic flair, and my sophisticated transition lenses. 😎 I'm ready for sailing in style! 🛥 #OOTD #FashionBlogger #YachtClubCouture #RodeoBeachChic #90sVibes #WhoWhatWear #FootwearOnFleek #ClassicMan #SaltLife #FashionDads via @pennyhonda

location.location_name: North Shore Beach and Yacht Club

posts.caption: As a #DIY #LifestyleBlogger, my arts and crafts DO come first, but fashion is a very close second! 💁🏼 You guys are always asking me what I wear when I'm in #WorkMode, so I'm excited to reveal one of my favorite looks. First of all, short athletic shorts are a staple -- they provide comfort and mobility for everything you do, and I love to show off my shapely #YogaLegs. 😊 I also love to go #monochromatic these days, so I chose a chic and breathable lime green tee to match my #Nike shorts. Mark my words -- bold greens are fresh off the runway and guaranteed to be one of this season's hottest hues! 💚💚💚 And this custom-designed tool belt is really adding some rugged flair to the ensemble, don't you think? 😎💅🏻 #OOTD #WhatIWore #WorkFlow #AllGreenEverything #DIYlife #Pinterest #BlessedToBlog #Fashion #Style #RunwayReady #FashionDads via @hdunham

I always say “Don’t let anyone dull your sparkle” 💫 and this #CycloneBomb won’t keep me from showing off my tan and toned gams! 💁🏼 It may not feel like #ShortsWeather but if you keep your core warm with a puffer coat like this orange #Patagonia stunner, you’d be surprised at how toasty the rest of your body will be. 🔥 I was dying to break out these bold #Bermuda shorts with a chic blue tube sock and my signature white #Keds, and the combination did not disappoint! With this versatile look, I’m truly ready for anything, from an après ski happy hour to a bowling night out to a simple strut around my cul de sac. Stay warm out there, fellow fashionistas! ❄️ #OOTD #BombCyclone #BombOutfit 💣 #LegDay #WhoWhatWear #Versatility #BoldColors #PlaiddyIssues #BermudaVibes #LoveYourLook #WinterWear #FashionDads via @harry.danielson_

The weather is unseasonably warm so what better time to break out some fun, flirty prints? 😊💅🏻 When I mix patterns, I go all the way, head-to-toe, because true #fashionistas never half-a$$ it. 🙊 So today I've paired a trendy plaid #BermudaShort from #BoldNavy with a tropical #PacSun button-down and a stylish ruby red belt from (you guessed it) #Ferragamo! 🌺🌸 I've treated my feet with custom #DrSuess socks and a pair of chic @toms #espadrilles in a sassy plaid print. This look can transition perfectly from a casual cookout to a swanky rooftop party, and you never know where #SundayFunday could take you! 😎😉 #OOTD #MixingPrints #SpringtimeVibes #PlaiddyIssues #Pinterest #ClassicMan #FunAndFlirty #SpringLookbook #SkiesOutThighsOut #TreesOutKneesOut 🌳#TreatYourFeet #TransitionalPieces #FashionBlogger #TapForTags #FashionDads

My team may not be in the #SuperBowl, but you best believe I'm still supporting them with this stunning ensemble. 💁🏼🐬🐬 This is a head-to-toe #DolphinsDiva outfit, custom made by my good friend and talented #Miami designer Dan Perino. The blouse is a high-quality dryfit material and the shorts are a beautiful and breathable cotton blend. And because I always commit to my couture, I completed this look with matching socks, sassy sneakers, a ball cap, and yes, even a trendy unisex bracelet! That frumpy Bill Belichick could definitely take some fashion tips from me! 😎 #OOTD #SuperBowlSwag #TeamTrends #CustomCouture #DanPerino #LacesOut #Accessorizing #MiamiStyle #DiveIntoFashion #FashionDads
@middleclassfancy, you speak to our soul 🙌🏼😭🔥 @middleclassfancy
No one understands us like @middleclassfancy 😭👟🙌🏼 we die every time

LOL one of my fans spotted me today and sent me this pic! I love when you guys catch me in action. 😎 Today while picking up a new mobile phone at #Walmart, I chose a fairly low-key ensemble (you know I dress up for more Target, though! 😜). I paired a trendy, mid-rise #Puma athletic short with a bold yellow blouse (tucked in, of course) from #TJMaxx because bright colors are so on-trend right now. For footwear, I'm donning a classic pair of #Birkenstocks, THE must-have shoe for spring and summer, and I completed the look with a chic ball cap that really ties everything together. Sorry if I made you jealous, Walmart shoppers! 😜 #OOTD #FanLove #FashionBlogger #StreetStyle #WhatIWore #Maxxinista #BoldColors #PumaByRihanna #FootwearOnFleek #BirkItAndTwerkIt #FashionDads via @faithfuldog
Those khakis and skate loafers tho! WHOSE DAD IS THIS?? 😭😩😎 video courtesy of @cas_primos

Big reveal time! 😱 I am SO excited to show you guys my new #WaistTrainer -- I can already feel it working off these wine calories. 😜😜🍷 I chose a chic blue trainer from the Hourglass Angel sport collection and I just love how it complements my wardrobe. Today I'm wearing a contemporary t-shirt from my favorite vineyard paired with relaxed fit #Lee jeans (that probably won't fit me much longer if the Kardashians have taught me anything!! 💁🏼). I completed this look with a sassy straw #fedora and all-purpose #Asics trainers. And the neutral elbow brace really ties everything together. Cheers, dolls! #OOTD #WaistTraining #HourglassAngel #KardashianVibes #SkinnyJeans #LifestyleBlogger #WineTime #VineyardChic #ReadyForTheWeekend #FashionDads via @karmastead

Phew, what a weekend! I absolutely love staying active on Saturdays and Sundays, so it’s crucial I wear a versatile ensemble that can take me from the streets to the seashore. 💁🏼🌊 You’ll notice that I paired a sleek below-the-knee board short with a trendy rash guard blouse by my favorite outdoor designer #LandsEnd. 🙌🏻 With a lewk like this, I can go straight from Sunday brunch to a quick dip in the ocean or even a jaunt to the outlets for some shopping. And as always, my neon #Asics sneakers are making a powerful statement of comfort + couture. 😊 Top it all off with some wraparound #StunnerShades and you’ll be turning heads all around town. 😎 #OOTD #WeekendFlow #Activewear #WhatIWore #SurfStyle #BoardShorts #RashionFashion #CoastalCouture #RunwayReady #SundaySwag #FashionDads via @georgie.mckay

Attention fashionistas: #UggSeason is coming to a close so get in your wears while you can!! Today I'm doing a casual and contemporary look with my fave #camel colored #Uggs -- straight-leg dark denim #Levis (always a classic!) with a fabulous plaid button-down straight off the #EddieBauer runway at #FashionWeek. 💃🏼 And I always love to don a sassy accessory so today it's a vintage #VonDutch trucker hat (they never go out of style!). This look can transition from exploring the outdoors to happy hour martinis, which I definitely plan on doing! 😉🍸 #OOTD #FridayFlow #UggLove #InMyLevis #PlaiddyIssues #OutdoorCouture #FashionBlogger #WhatIWore #StyleFiles #AccessoriesAreEverything #FashionDads via @vsillars

Weekends are for style AND comfort -- find you a #fashionista who can do both. 💁🏼 Today I have paired two of my favorite wardrobe staples, black #IvyPark leggings (thanks Bey 😉) and a short-sleeved #sherling vest from #Ugg (can you believe these ahhh-mazing pockets?!). 😊 You can never go wrong with chic, classic pieces like these, and you can always add your own signature flair like this #vintage T-Rex tee and fabulous fur slippers with cozy crew socks. When we head out to Red Lobster tonight, I may slip on a pair of trendy loafers or my classic white #NewBalance trainers, just depends on my mood! 💅🏻 #OOTD #WeekendFlow #ClassicMan #LeggingLove #FurOnFleek #FashionAndFunction #CuttingEdgeTrends #RexyAndIKnowIt #FashionDads

WHEW we have quite a nor'easter brewing and it is crucial that you dress accordingly, but still stick to your sassy signature style! 💨 I love to wear heavy-duty basics with a dash of fun flair when I face the elements -- always putting the "fun" in functional, amirite?! 💅🏻Today I have chosen a custom pair of #Spongebob FlairPants 😜 and my chic #Grinch #TruckerHat to complement my #KennethCold puffer jacket and #Brrrberry galoshes. 👢👢 The way the neighbors are admiring me, you might call me the eye of the storm. 😉 #OOTD #WinterWear #StormStyle #BootSeason #GaloshesGoals #SpongebobSquareDad #FroidFrashion ❄️ #CuteCoats #PuffDaddy #ChicAndTrendy #FashionDads via @bethany.douglas17

What a DAY! I am feeling so #blessed to celebrate #FathersDay in Florida in such a fabulous ensemble. 😎 I always like to mix in a splash of silly with my style on holidays, so today was the perfect opportunity to wear this custom t-shirt from #PacificPunwear. 😎💨I paired it with a stunning but simple cargo short from #AmericanEagle and my signature #Teva sandals (had to leave the #Gucci loafers back at the hotel in this warm weather 💁🏼). I spiced things up even more with a chic #Pokémon ball cap and a subtle orange bracelet because accessories truly are everything. Happy Dad's Day to all the fashionable fathers out there werking it like me! 👊🏼 #OOTD #WhatIWore #FathersDayFashion #VacayVibes #BeachLooks #FloridaStyle #FunAndFashion #WorldsBestFarter #CargoCouture #SandalSwag #FunInTheSun #FashionDads via @laura_n_desisto
